AI_AVATAR_STYLE_PROMPT="Style requirements: centered profile avatar, clean background, high contrast, no text, no watermark, square framing."
AI_CHAT_IMAGE_EDIT_STYLE_PROMPT="Edit only what the user asked. Keep subject identity and original composition, no text or watermark."
